data.description: DEEP WATER,SAILBOAT ACCESS WATERFRONT HOME W/BRAND NEW COMPOSITE DOCK & CONCRETE SEAWALL.2 CANALS AWAY FROM THE "BIG WATER".NO HOA AND NO DEED RESTRICTIONS!This large home has 4 bedrms (or 3 bedrms with In Law suite),office,LR,DR,KIT w SS appl & eating area(aquarium window)near the lg FR w/ built ins.Sliders off the LR that disappear, 8' sliders in the FR, French doors in the MBED & in the kit.The spacious lanai area will be great for entertaining overlooking the pool w/ fountain.It also has a private pool bath.The overwhelming water views of the canal are seen from almost every room.This home has cat 5 impact windows in the DR, OFF & MBATH.It also has 11' ceilings in the oversized GAR with attic ladder & water softner. PRICE REDUCED/OWNER IS MOTIVATED This home has a oversized paver driveway with an RV dump drain & 30 amp plug.Hurricane steel brackets for the garage door. New hurricane accordion shutters 2023, lanai rescreen 2022, front screen 2022, roof, soffit, gutters & facia 10/22, new composite dock 11/22, concrete seawall 10/22, water heater 2020, washer & dryer 2021.Flood insurance is $866 and transferrable.VA ASSUMABLE @ 2.75% ON $438K.  VET NEEDS COE + DIFFERENCE.
